window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mrs Zant has recently lost her beloved husband, and while walking in the Kensington Gardens, the spot where she and her deceased husband declared their love for each other, she feels his presence trying to warn her of some coming danger. </p> <p>Mr Rayburn witnesses it all, and he'll have to fight his own incredulity regarding the supernatural and his gut feeling that the disturbed young woman is telling the truth. </p> <p>Brought to life by Golden Globe Award-winning actress Gillian Anderson (<i>The X-Files</i>), Mrs Zant is the perfect Victorian ghost story. </p>"; 
